.\}
.nf
Da XIQueryPointa function returns tha root window the
device\*(Aqs pointa is logically on n' tha pointa coordinates
relatizzle ta tha root window\*(Aqs origin\&. If XIQueryPointa returns
False, tha pointa aint on tha same screen as tha specified
window, n' XIQueryPointa returns None ta child_return and
zero ta win_x_return n' win_y_return\&. If XIQueryPointer
returns True, tha pointa coordinates moonwalked back ta win_x_return
and win_y_return is relatizzle ta tha origin of tha specified
window\&. In dis case, XIQueryPointa returns tha lil pimp that
gotz nuff tha pointer, if any, or else None ta child_return\&.
.fi
.if n \{\
